   0a8a   30 8e             BR MM_DO_CLEAR_CASTLE
                        
   0a8c                 MM_CLEAR_BLACK_CASTLE:
   0a8c   f8 0c             LDI $0C             ; CASTLE_BK ($04) + CASTLE_BQ ($08)
                        
