   0c05   d5                SEP 5
                        
                        ; ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                        ; MM_ROOK_HOME_CHECK - Check if square is a rook home square
                        ; ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                        ; If so, clear the corresponding castling right.
                        ; Input: D = square to check
                        ; Clobbers: R10, R13 (via CLEAR_CASTLING_RIGHT)
