   0c2e                 UNMAKE_MOVE:
                            ; DIAG stamp (2026-07-17 hang hunt).
   0c2e   68 c9 64 1d       RLDI 9, TRACE_WHERE
   0c32   f8 a4             LDI $A4
   0c34   59                STR 9               ; tracer: in UNMAKE_MOVE (R9 reloaded below)
                        
